[
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wei_shi",
    "text": "潜龙来过了咱们这儿？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 16,
    "line_end": 18
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "是呀，昨晚闹了个天翻地覆呢？不过，待我们出来的时候，那潜龙早已不见了。所以详情我也不知。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 20,
    "line_end": 20
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这算是你的运气，要是你碰上了潜龙，你还能活在这里说话吗？郡马，你恐怕还未知道呢，咱们院中本领最强的两个高手听说都已丧生在潜龙手下了。",
    "tone": "大笑",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 22,
    "line_end": 24
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "卫士",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "王爷正在大发脾气，郡马，你快去劝解劝解，否则我们只怕有许多人要倒霉了。",
    "tone": "焦急",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 28,
    "line_end": 30
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "你们这许多人都是只会吃饭的吗？一条潜龙也捉不住！",
    "tone": "愤怒",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 34,
    "line_end": 34
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "是，是。我们没用，惹得王爷生气。但这条潜龙，实在是厉害得很，封老头和祈老二都给他杀了！",
    "tone": "恐惧",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 36,
    "line_end": 38
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "建侯，我知道你已经尽了力了，这也怪不得你。说起来还是我的责任，我已经知道'潜龙'潜入了大都，却未够小心防备。倘若我昨晚在这儿，总不能让他这样容易跑掉。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 50,
    "line_end": 52
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "王爷是咱们大金的第一高手，王爷若在这儿，潜龙纵有天大的神通也是跑不掉的。不过，王爷日理万机，军国大事都是担在王爷肩上。研经院虽然重要，却也不能要王爷在这里坐镇。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 54,
    "line_end": 56
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "是呀，我就是因为不能在院中坐镇，又怕潜龙还会再来，是以甚感焦虑。建侯，你找几个本领好而又靠得住的人来，咱们大家商议商议补救的办法吧。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 64,
    "line_end": 66
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "郡马又聪明又沉着，又是自己人，院中出了这样的大事，你可得多费点心，给你的岳父大人出出主意了。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 68,
    "line_end": 70
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "世雄，内举不避亲，我也是一向看重你的，你就不必推辞了。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 72,
    "line_end": 74
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "好，建侯，你先报告昨晚的详细情形。你们见着了'潜龙'没有？他到底是怎样的一个人？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 90,
    "line_end": 92
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "在场人员",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "我到来的时候，只听得封祈二人惨厉的叫声，我忙着救护他们，无暇去追潜龙。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 96,
    "line_end": 98
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_wei_shi",
    "text": "封老头和祈老二临死之时可有说话留下？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 102,
    "line_end": 104
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "在场人员",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "我把他们扶起之时，他们都已气绝。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 106,
    "line_end": 108
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wei_shi",
    "speaker_name": "在场人员",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "潜龙跑得太快，我追不上，只见着两条黑影，越过假山，转眼间就消失了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 110,
    "line_end": 112
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_wei_shi",
    "text": "什么，有两条黑影？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 114,
    "line_end": 114
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "不错，除了潜龙之外，还有一个女子。我刚才正要禀告王爷——",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 116,
    "line_end": 116
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "哦，原来你看见他们了。",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 118,
    "line_end": 118
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "可惜我也只是见着他们的背影，从背影辨得出，其中一个乃是女子。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 120,
    "line_end": 120
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "这么说来，潜龙大闹了研经院，你们竟是连他的面都没有见着。",
    "tone": "无奈",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 122,
    "line_end": 124
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "卑职无能，截不住潜龙。不过，他们之中，也有一个着了我的飞刀。",
    "tone": "尴尬",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 128,
    "line_end": 130
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "是男的还是女的？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 132,
    "line_end": 134
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "他们正逃入花树丛中，我的飞刀掷出，只听见哎哟一声，却不知道是着了哪一个。不过，听那叫声，却是男子，多半是潜龙着了我的飞刀了。我的飞刀，是取对方上盘的，倘不是斫着头颅，就是斫着肩头。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 136,
    "line_end": 136
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "潜龙既然还能逃走，当然是斫着肩头了。好，这倒是一条线索。",
    "tone": "冷静",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 138,
    "line_end": 138
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "看来潜龙好像很熟悉研经院中的道路，要不然决不能如此容易跑掉。",
    "tone": "犹豫",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 140,
    "line_end": 142
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "text": "倘真如此，这就要更小心防备了。你们有什么好办法没有？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 146,
    "line_end": 148
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "潜龙的目标是这间密室，我以为首先应该换过这里的机关。",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 152,
    "line_end": 154
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "对。你的大师父不但武功高强，他也是最擅长布置机关的，你可曾学过他这门功夫？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 156,
    "line_end": 156
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "大师父的本事我可没有学全，只得八成功夫。",
    "tone": "谦虚",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 160,
    "line_end": 160
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_ban_jian_hou",
    "speaker_name": "班建侯",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你大师父布置机关的本领天下无双，你有八成的功夫，那是很不错了。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 160,
    "line_end": 160
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "好，既然你懂得布置机关，那就不必客气了。赶快给我绘图，咱们把研经院中的机关全都换过。限你今天一天之内，设计妥当，成吗？",
    "tone": "认真",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 162,
    "line_end": 162
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "text": "小婿尽力而为，晚一点回家，我想是可以成的。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 164,
    "line_end": 164
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wan_yan_chang_zhi",
    "speaker_name": "完颜长之",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "这些机关果然新奇，潜龙若敢再来，那是一定逃不掉的了。好，你赶快回去吧，凤儿只怕已经等得心焦了。",
    "tone": "欣喜",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 168,
    "line_end": 168
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "text": "对不住，劳你久等了。",
    "tone": "轻笑",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 176,
    "line_end": 178
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_meng_zhong_huan",
    "speaker_name": "孟中还",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "没什么，上车吧。嗯，今天天气很热，请郡马恕我粗鲁。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 182,
    "line_end": 184
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你回来了？",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 198,
    "line_end": 198
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "是呀，院中出了大事，所以我回来晚了。",
    "tone": "陈述",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 200,
    "line_end": 200
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "是么？什么事情，明天你再告诉我吧。小凤出了水痘，我不放心奶妈照料，我想去陪她几晚。",
    "tone": "淡然",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 202,
    "line_end": 204
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "speaker_name": "鲁世雄",
    "listener": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "text": "啊，小凤出了水痘了？我和你去看她吧。",
    "tone": "担心",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 208,
    "line_end": 208
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_du_gu_fei_feng",
    "speaker_name": "独孤飞凤",
    "listener": "char_lu_shi_xiong",
    "text": "你累了，还是早点安歇吧。你又不会照料孩子，反而吵了小凤。你放心，我已经给她拿了药了，这是父王让御医所配的药，一定会治好小凤的。",
    "tone": "温柔",
    "chapter": 6,
    "line_start": 210,
    "line_end": 210
  }
]